CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FTwo men have been been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder and three others guilty of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter after the death of a 24-
OL,9,Fyear-old in Exmouth last year.
OL,11,FDenva Smith died from a stab wound to
OL,12,Fhis arm in the early hours of 31 May
OL,13,F2025, after being chased through the
OL,14,Fstreets into a garden where he bled to
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,FThomas Ward, 25, delivered the killer
OL,18,Fblow to his former friend. Ben Mason,
OL,19,F24, chased the injured Denva from
OL,20,FDinan Way to Ashfield Close.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
