OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FBoth men denied murder but were found
OL,7,Fguilty after a trial.
OL,9,F24-year-old Zac Davies (of Hawthorn
OL,10,FGrove, Exmouth), 24-year-old Dylan
OL,11,FChadwick (of Cambourne Avenue, St
OL,12,FHelens) and 27-year-old Ben Helliker
OL,13,F(of Halsdon Road, Exmouth) were part
OL,14,Fof the group attack and have been
OL,15,Ffound guilty of manslaughter.
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Guy Biggar, of the
OL,18,FForce's Major Crime Investigation
OL,19,FTeam, said: "We welcome the verdicts
OL,20,Freached by the jury at Exeter Crown
OL,21,FCourt today.
OL,26,@{D@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with Denva Smith's
OL,7,Ffamily, and I would like to thank them
OL,8,Ffor their support and immense strength
OL,9,Fthroughout this investigation and
OL,10,Ftrial."
OL,12,FAt the end of the trial, the judge
OL,13,Fsaid he intended to give an official
OL,14,Fcommendation to a witness who tried to
OL,15,Fhelp Denva as he lay dying in the
OL,16,Fgarden. He also praised detectives for
OL,17,Ftheir investigation.
OL,19,FMr Justice Garnham told the jury:
OL,20,F"This has been an extraordinarily
OL,21,Fdifficult and complex case."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FHe praised the jury for their
OL,7,Fattentiveness during the seven-week
OL,8,Ftrial. He said he would not proceed
OL,9,Fstraight to sentence and needed time
OL,10,Fto reflect on the circumstances.
OL,11,FAccording to him, sentencing should
OL,12,Ftake place at the beginning of May.
OL,14,FThe trial was told there was a
OL,15,Fbackground of revenge and drug rivalry
OL,16,Fto the killing. Denva had "beaten up"
OL,17,FMason a few days before, and he had
OL,18,Fsworn payback. Both Ward and Mason
OL,19,Fwere said to "have beef" with Denva.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FWard, who had once been Denva's best
OL,7,Ffriend, said they had fallen out after
OL,8,Fhe started a relationship with Denva's
OL,9,Fex partner.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said the five men
OL,12,Fplanned to attack Denva on the night
OL,13,Fof his death and steal his stash of
OL,14,Fcocaine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FShortly after 12.30am, Denva and a
OL,7,Ffriend were walking along Dinan Way
OL,8,Fwhen they encountered the five men
OL,9,Fwalking towards them. Denva bolted
OL,10,Fdown a grass roadside embankment where
OL,11,Fhe came face-to-face with Ward who
OL,12,Fstabbed him in the arm.
OL,14,FWard said it happened quickly and he
OL,15,Fthought he was going to be attacked.
OL,16,FDenva fell down the bank before
OL,17,Fgetting to his feet and running along
OL,18,FHawthorn Grove and into Ashfield Close.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FHe was chased by Mason and Chadwick
OL,7,Finto a garden where he collapsed and
OL,8,Fbled to death. He spent his final
OL,9,Fmoments shouting for help, awakening
OL,10,Fthe owner and their neighbours.
OL,12,FThe attackers who had chased Denva
OL,13,Falong Ashfield Close left the scene
OL,14,Fand rejoined the others in the group.
OL,15,FThey then returned to the scene of
OL,16,Fattack where they picked up Denva's
OL,17,Fshoes, which he lost on the
OL,18,Fembankment, and later dumped them in a
OL,19,Fbin.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FPolice first responders arrived at the
OL,7,Fgarden in under 10 minutes, followed
OL,8,Fby paramedics. Denva managed to
OL,9,Fprovide his name and state that he had
OL,10,Fbeen stabbed before passing out. He
OL,11,Fwas pronounced dead in the garden at
OL,12,F1:40am.
OL,14,FA few hours before he was killed,
OL,15,FDenva is said to have seen Mason in
OL,16,Fthe town centre where they exchanged
OL,17,Finsults.
OL,19,FWard knew Denva Smith, and had a child
OL,20,Fwith a woman who had previously had a
OL,21,Fchild with Denva.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FChadwick and Davies had come to
OL,7,FExmouth that evening from Liverpool
OL,8,Fand met up with Helliker, Mason and
OL,9,FWard around 30 minutes before the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FDenva Smith's blood was found on Zac
OL,13,FDavies' and Benjamin Mason's shoes and
OL,14,Fon Dylan Chadwick's shoes and trousers.
OL,16,FDetectives and CPS built a case around
OL,17,Fphone data and CCTV footage gathered
OL,18,Fduring the investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,FCharlotte Ream of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service said: "Denva Smith
OL,8,Fwas the victim of a brutal, targeted
OL,9,Fattack that tragically ended his life.
OL,11,F"The Crown Prosecution Service worked
OL,12,Fclosely with our colleagues in Devon
OL,13,Fand Cornwall Police to build our case.
OL,14,FThis showed that all five men acted
OL,15,Ftogether to carry out the attack, and
OL,16,Fthat they therefore share joint
OL,17,Fresponsibility for Denva's death.
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773411079
OL,3,CTwo men guilty of murdering 24-year-
OL,4,Cold in 'brutal targeted' group attack
OL,6,F"In cases like these, we have to prove
OL,7,Fto the jury that each defendant played
OL,8,Fan active part in the fatal attack,
OL,9,Fnot just that they were there.
OL,11,F"Thanks to a thorough police
OL,12,Finvestigation we were able build a
OL,13,Fcomprehensive picture of the five
OL,14,Fmen's movements that night and the
OL,15,Frole they played.
OL,17,F"Today's verdicts are a reminder that
OL,18,Fthe carrying of knives can only lead
OL,19,Fto tragedy and our thoughts remain
OL,20,Fwith Denva's family and loved ones,
OL,21,Fincluding his young children."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
